reviewText: A great Christmas movie for the family.
This is a super great movie for the family. We have watched it numerous times. Highly recommend this one.
The audio doesn't match the mouth movements.  You can tell foreign language is spoke by the actors while what you hear is English....a little awkward to watch but, a nice plot regardless.

This is a story that could have been good, sans the drinking (drunk santa) and other obnoxious elements.  I sure wasn't expecting the poor
(Godzilla type) voiceovers.  The kid was cute, the story line had potential, the product was a complete disaster and I am not at all happy that I purchased it.  This goes to the trash.  I would not inflict this on another person and CERTAINLY not children!

10/10 for the animatronic moose used in this film, 6/10 for the story, 9/10 for the execution.

This is  a dutch film, I really enjoyed watching it with english subtitles though; everyone's voice sounded much better in their natural language, especially the moose!

This is pretty much a made-for-TV quality film. The ending is just great though.
Cute Christmas movie.
